    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the potatoes have 10 min left, line the reserved baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and put the tray in the oven for 12 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
