    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cod is almost ready, return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, remove the pan from the heat and add the <strong>sliced spring greens</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Return the pan to the heat and cook for 2-3 min or until wilted</p>",
